<h1 class="h1">Media</h1>
<p class="lead">Audio/Video-Einbindungen (YouTube, SoundCloud, etc.) – einfach Links einsetzen.</p>

<div class="grid">
  <div class="card">
    <h2 class="h2">Video</h2>
    <p class="small muted">Beispiel: YouTube-Embed (ersetze die Video-ID).</p>
    <div style="position:relative;padding-top:56.25%;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--line)">
      <iframe
        title="YouTube"
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VIDEO_ID"
        style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;border:0"
        loading="lazy"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2 class="h2">Audio</h2>
    <p class="small muted">Beispiel: SoundCloud (ersetze den Link im iframe).</p>
    <iframe
      title="SoundCloud"
      width="100%"
      height="166"
      scrolling="no"
      frameborder="no"
      allow="autoplay"
      src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=..."
      style="border-radius:16px;border:1px solid var(--line)"
    ></iframe>
  </div>
</div>
